paragraphs.text: everybody's talking but i'm out of attention i can only feel the information passing by i'm deep inside a bubble and there's no one here to shout me out the storm inside my head got me tossing and turning each and every night i've been a victim of my brain i know i've got to take a rest but i just don't know how
my twisted universe just won't let me go it finally got me on my knees
please please please i don't need another night like that please please please leave me alone and don't you dare to come back i don't want you you just came to keep me awake
